Ifeoma Nnenna Dieke (amụrụ na 25 Febụwarị 1981) bụ onye na-agbachitere bọọlụ bọọlụ na Scotland nke a mụrụ na America, na-egwuri egwu ugbu a maka Apollon Ladies F.C
Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka ọtụtụ klọb ndị ọkachamara na Sweden na United Steeti
N'agbata afọ 2004 na afo 2017, ọ meriri ugboro ato maka otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Scotland

A mụrụ Dieke na Amherst, Massachusetts, nne na nna Naijiria, ọ kwagara Cumbernauld na Scotland mgbe ọ dị afọ atọ. Dieke na onye Scot ibe ya Kim Little bụ naanị ndị egwuregwu na-abụghị ndị Bekee ahọpụtara na ndị otu Great Britain maka 2012 London Olympics.
Na Jenụwarị ago 2018, Dieke hapụrụ Vittsjö mgbe oge isii gasịrị

N'ịchọ ihe ịma aka ọhụrụ, ọ sonyeere klọb Damallsvenkan nke a na-akwalite ọhụrụ IFK Kalmar. Ọganihu ahụ enweghị ihe ịga nke ọma na Kalmar na-agagharị n'okpuru tebụl league, a chụpụrụ Dieke n'òtù ahụ ma hapụ ya n'oge ezumike n'etiti oge
A kọrọ na obi adịghị ya ụtọ na Kalmar enweghị ike iwusi ndị otu egwuregwu ha ike. Ọ laghachiri Apollon na Septemba 2018.

Dieke ruru eru ịnọchite anya Scotland, United States ma ọ bụ Nigeria na mba ụwa. O mere nke mbụ ya na Scotland na Jenụwarị na afo 2004 megide Gris ma nweta akara nke iri ise ya megide Northern Ireland na afo Mee 2009.
A na-akpọkarị Dieke "Ife" (ma ọ bụ "Iffy"). Ọ nwere ike ịsụ asụsụ Igbo.
